node.text:
Exercise 💪🏻can boost your immune system and reduce inflammation.
⠀
Exercise might be the single greatest “🌡medicine” to prevent illness.
You’ve 🤓probably heard all this before?
⠀
You might have tried😅 to go to a gym.
You lost 😩interest and got no results or life got in the way and you stopped going.
⠀
I have a program and it’s totally free. Why not try the first 😜workout with me?
You’re in your own home, no one to judge you.
And, I’m there doing every 💪🏻rep and every set with you.
How about giving one workout a try? Link in my bio😘
⠀
⠀

node.text:
Once upon a ⌛️time there was a fire 🔥 girl. 
People always wanted to change something in her.  But one day she was stolen by a 🐉 dragon. 
And he loved 🖤everything about her: how she 💥lights up, how she 🔥burns, and all her smoke🌪
